parcel.name: BITPIXI'S BAR 🧚‍♀️🍺
parcel.label: bar
parcel.description:
Press space bar to jump when the beat drops!
Past music performances by TipYourDJDotETH, R3LL, Weinbagz, ChadXP, ITSOKTOCRY (Gwen Stacy), and Dyl (Crypto Rich). Hosted official Deadheads reveal party, MetaMural Fest, Sewer Rats Social Club, Pulyxx Foundation drop, LemurLemur mint party, Just Bees, and now a total DRKNSS takeover!

Bitpixi works for Cryptovoxels, so this will be a historic place. Resell the free drinks for any price you'd like!

features.text:
#What is Bitpixi's Bar?

A place to connect globally for live music in the metaverse. A place to discover what Cryptovoxels is all about. A place to chill, have a drink, and vibe!

Our main DJ is TipYourDJDotETH and we have also featured performances by R3LL, Weinbagz, ChadXP, ITSOKTOCRY (Gwen Stacy), and Dyl (Crypto Rich).

Hosted official Deadheads reveal, MetaMural Fest, Sewer Rats Social Club, Pulyxx drop, LemurLemur mint, Just Bees collection, a DRKNSS takeover, and more.

@ bitpixi on Twitter to ask about your project proposal. bitpixi also works for CV now as Product Designer, and you can report bugs in the Discord, thanks.


++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

#Today we are featuring:


The zoo crew, ok it's LemurLemur, MetaSharks, Super Yetis, and Monster Shelter. 

We've got Wild Party DAO giving back $$ and voting rights to it's members, ran by TipYourDJDotETH aka PurpLeTariat our regular. Please connect with him if you're into music NFTs.

I also have up here some JPG people,  0n1Force, and my own voxel wearables. 

Lastly, I'm featuring the gnomes that keep stealing my kid's socks. No that's not an NFT collection. It's just a fact.

Why are you still reading this.

collectible.name: 32X32 bitpixi
collectible.description: Builder turned web team at Cryptovoxels, bitpixi works with one hand while holding her baby Rye in the other. This is the first fem in the series and a tribute to all working crypto moms, such as Stellabelle (as bitpixi has often adopted her signature tears motif)! May voxels always soften sadness. <3
